#####################################  How to make connection with mysql/MariaDB using python3 ################################

1st You need to check python3 version by using the command in ubuntu.
---------------------------------------------------------------------
python3 --version
---------------------------------------------------------------------
2nd You need to check mysql or mariaDB module installed on your ubuntu machine.
---------------------------------------------------------------------
pip3 list | grep PyMySQL
---------------------------------------------------------------------
